title: [Great Cavern, Bog]
description: There must be a stone floor beneath the mist here, but it is covered by thick, oozing mud.  You might step down into it to find out how deep it goes, but a little voice tells you that you are better off keeping to the firmer spots.  Odd sounds reverberate through the dark mist, continuing too long to be echos.
paths: Obvious exits: east, south, west, up
